gold;\">#毋忘葉虎事件！（疑似中聯辦指揮黑社會打人）大家可以幫推，甚至可以做埋社區文宣煲大佢，絕對唔可以比呢單野不了了之！</span><br />\n［緊急］點解葉虎單嘢可以不了了之？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1382778\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1382778</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#仲有84比海綿子彈爆頭暈倒義士、83有義士比狗圍住唔比食哮喘藥結果腦缺氧暈倒，728上環比橡膠子彈爆頭暈倒義士，希望你地可以平安萬全</span>"},{"pid":"60843e6ae11a5415d2c9f3d211c359eb0b793b7c","tid":1417450,"uid":12023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:23:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f9a13b7a0003927afa4a7a91dab6548b46155e11","tid":1417450,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41622099412b9c589edba81243508579a8831f7a","tid":1417450,"uid":12023,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d752271e11e927ae7679e981d1507ecd30bec75a","tid":1417450,"uid":201374,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:43:42.000Z","msg":"每次有人話放火掟警署燒警署暴力<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記得反問佢掟中燒中幾多個警察</span></span>，再講返每次有幾多手足頭破血流<br />\n咁都冇人復仇上心襲擊行街警察，只係破壞警署，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">代表我哋係用破壞警署嚟表達對整個軍警政權嘅不滿</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我哋正正係對準用黑警暴力打壓市民發聲嘅政權，而唔係針對警察發洩怒氣，所以先攻擊警署唔攻擊警察</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:48:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:38:20.000Z","msg":"當大家決定要去佔路、不合作運動的時候，已經唔會佔到道德高地"},{"pid":"9c673e0b06c7f274e60bb503d7b7f113ff665a75","tid":1417450,"uid":281467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"唔好自亂陣腳<br />\n<br />\n不分化 不割蓆<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力<br />\n<br />\n梁天琦: 不要被仇恨支配自己<br />\n<br />\n政治的工作不只是要令支持自己的人繼續支持自己，<br />\n<br />\n而更是要令不支持自己的人轉為支持自己，改變想法，認同自己的方向。"},{"pid":"2b992db8c1a2822d9b74ac4a9510b3dd03011236","tid":1417450,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"072bdf29ddf32e162f2002169b8a79bc8e250f9a","tid":1417450,"uid":55775,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:44:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:39:44.000Z","msg":"每個夜深，左膠post、三毛post、民意post，又全面進場"},{"pid":"0b65f69b82ea53ffd37a5e9c585b798964bc08e0","tid":1417450,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d976e922fd2a67462cb4b295d69bd3120e7e5cf2","tid":1417450,"uid":156298,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:47:55.000Z","msg":"是實上不合作運動係消耗緊自己人既民意. 對成個運動幫助唔大.<br />\n一日半日, 自己人當然冇問題, 唔同路既只會更憎你. <br />\n今日周圍都係啲呀叔講, 你表達意見冇問題, 你唔好攪交通嘛..<br />\n如果攪交通係有用, 我覺得應該去攪, 但似乎真係冇乜用.<br />\n而罷工, 真係唔可以逼人罷. 於事無補. <br />\n反而個個星期係7區唔同地方申請不反對通知書, 佢總唔可以區區都唔批, 到時先吹雞集中去一個地方, 咁就名正言順. 集會完左, 前線打游擊都點到即止, 咁就冇咁多料比人做. <br />\n<br />\n不如真心諗下想做到乜<br />\n1. 等警隊疲於奔命, 犯大錯, keep民意支持<br />\n2. 癱瘓香港, 大家一鑊熟 (一定冇民意)<br />\n3. 同警察硬碰硬, 不理傷亡<br />\n4. 打持久戰, keep住daily headline都係 protest<br />\n<br />\n而家係以上四樣都做緊.. 係好矛盾的."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:40:33.000Z","msg":"連不合作運動都消耗民意，無野下話?????"},{"pid":"d88a20b41810b6c7a110e9d378f94d5e1e08001d","tid":1417450,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d44bc1f923547dca6eb782cc52320a9454e9e98","tid":1417450,"uid":268342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:48:31.000Z","msg":"變陣，要普選一定要同嗰幾十高官講，嗰千幾個選委講，用對警方既力道，和平地同佢地表達市民訴求。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:41:18.000Z","msg":"不如又200萬人和平上街遊行啦? 一定有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d21949365e5a3994dd591624ab5efac1e848ed","tid":1417450,"uid":131842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:41:21.000Z","msg":"全港流浪狗位置實時地圖上線啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/cAzgTon.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcAzgTon.png&h=5d46c5a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n是咁的，本人寫左個好似google doc咁既地圖<br />\n<br />\n睇緊live既即刻入黎幫手報料!<br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=d81b98cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a><br />\n見到多狗, 即刻mark番落地圖<br />\n視乎數量就算已經報左都可以報多一次<br />\n幫手傳出去 等義士唔好再食布袋戰術<br />\nBe Water!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1406448/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://hkmap.live/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhkmap.live%2F&d=aRHHWgZm4a4JNL46Iov0BPQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=d81b98cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hkmap.live/</a>"},{"pid":"7a4ded03772576bbe85f50943e827d85adb80176","tid":1417450,"uid":262799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"889d5eb260c456afab7b0efef8e267282b86e953","tid":1417450,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"25df50ac633364184d9c85ef959213c29fa0724f","tid":1417450,"uid":12023,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"072bdf29ddf32e162f2002169b8a79bc8e250f9a","tid":1417450,"uid":55775,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:44:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T16:54:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:42:39.000Z","msg":"不如號召返200萬人和平上街啦，一定集到民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f9d8df398afc5f3e5d03da805ab3226fa7d4c7","tid":1417450,"uid":244087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T17:43:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2ae19ba9234b7d70ba302ed3260beec5e83c4b4b","tid"